name: Grateful Guppy #21
description:
Mythosis timeline is set in the modern times where the presence of diwatas (nymphs) and deities in the human world have long passed, and memories of the past were already forgotten. Left with no idea of what darkness may come to them, and how to defend themselves from forgotten forces of evil: the humans are now in danger; the weakening of the barrier has started. The Malignos will be on their way. Mythosis supports Gratitude Gang!
